name: F.lifestage.passage
friendly: Estimates production by life stage and run.
description: Estimates production of all lifestages in all runs between two dates.

name: F.run.passage
description: Estimates production for ALL runs (all lifestages combined) between two dates.

name: F.allCatch.table
description: Produces a table of everything caught between two dates.  No summary or inflation.

name: F.byCatch.table
description: Produces a CSV file of daily non-Chinook catch (by-catch) between two dates.  No summary or inflation.

name: F.chinookByDate.table
description: Produces a table of daily chinook catch at all subsites-with marked and unmarked counts.

name: F.release.summary
description: Summarizes something cool about the fish and their release.

name: F.size.by.date
description: Plots fork length through time by age class.

name: F.length.frequency
description: Plots histograms of fork length with respect to age classes, or collapsed together.

name: F.weekly.effort
friendly: Plot the weekly effort over time.
description: Plot the weekly effort over time.

name: F.lifestage.passage.assignLS
friendly: Assigns lifestage, then estimates production by life stage and run.
description: Assigns life stage, then estimates production of all lifestages in all runs between two dates.
